name: Gamer NFLs
description: Non-Fungible Leets (NFLs) are randomly generated NFTs. Each of 10,000 battle-ready NFLs have inbuilt rarity determiners and are completely unique. If you are fortunate enough to mint one of these NFLs, you will be rewarded a 5% royalty on all future sales of your NFL and gain access to future exclusive areas of the GMR Center.
